name: value-pair
description: I am a simple man. When I see two values that need to be paired, I don’t want any overcomplicated module. This may be the simplest module you have ever downloaded, but it’s worth it. This Pair class can pair values. It’s just an object with a constructor, two attributes and debug print method.
